pascal said we certainly stand by our data and what we saw in 
these six states 
we chose six states that had different approaches to reform 
we didnt want to choose all the southern states she said 
to finns charge that just going along with reform was hardly 
praiseworthy mcdonnell said those reforms could not have been 
put in place had there not been accommodation and cooperation from 
the local teacher unions had the teacher unions wanted to 
sandbag them they probably could 
