operated at 815 percent of capacity up from 803 percent in 
march us utilities operated at an 811 percent rate last month 
down from 818 percent a month earlier 
the changes left the overall operating rate of 827 percent up 
sharply from a year earlier when american industry operated at 
796 percent of capacity 
