percent overall and 97 percent in the top four job categories to 
378 percent overall and 299 percent in top jobs 
for cable fcc figures show minorities going from 117 percent 
overall and 102 percent in the top four job categories in 1978 to 
195 percent overall and 157 percent in the top jobs in 1987 
