when steve wynn first visited here in 
1952 sharing his fathers dream of a flashy bingo parlor on a 
patch of desert called the strip 5 million could have bought the 
clump of casinos that captivated the 10yearold 
today wynn is spending more than a hundred times that amount on 
a desert paradise that staggers even his immense imagination a 
new golden nugget hotel and casino on the las vegas strip 
the youngster who was starstruck by this neon fantasyland 36 
